      </sectiondef>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Wakeup count class implemented according to C++ singleton design pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The class provides methods to handle the wakeup counter which is stored persitently in flash file system. Wakeup count is read at startup and </para>
</simplesect>
<xrefsect id="todo_1_todo000019"><xreftitle>Todo</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>is stored in private variable boot_count.</para>
</xrefdescription></xrefsect></para>
    </detaileddescription>
